                                    text="&lt;p>The &lt;b>AbbVie Foundation Health Equity Accelerator&lt;/b> in partnership with &lt;a href=&quot;https://matter.health/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>MATTER&lt;/a>, focuses on accelerating community-led, innovative solutions to advance health equity in underserved communities. The Accelerator identifies nonprofit organizations with innovative approaches to addressing inequities in their communities – and empowers them with essential grants, mentorship and resources to scale their initiatives and impact.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
